data.description: Welcome to the desirable Stone Lakes neighborhood!  This beautiful 4-bedroom home features hardwood floors, a spacious 2 car garage, and a finished basement perfect for entertainment or relaxation.  All bedrooms are located on the second floor!  Enjoy the privacy of a fenced yard and ample storage space for your belongings.  Conveniently located near Parklands, highways and schools, this property offers both convenience and practicality for you or your family's needs.  Stone Lakes offers multiple ponds, walking trails, and playgrounds for your outdoor enjoyment.  Do not miss the opportunity to make this your dream home!
